          <wm>http://www.npr.org/templates/dmg/dmg_wmref_em.php?id=133882154&amp;type=1&amp;mtype=WM&amp;orgId=1&amp;topicId=1052&amp;aggIds=5163715&amp;ft=3&amp;f=</wm>
          <rm>http://www.npr.org/templates/dmg/dmg_rpm.rpm?id=133882154&amp;type=1&amp;mtype=RM&amp;orgId=1&amp;topicId=1052&amp;aggIds=5163715&amp;ft=3&amp;f=</rm>
